1410
02:34:23,110 --> 02:34:24,610
Đúng vậy. Làm đi.

1411
02:34:29,360 --> 02:34:30,650
Xin chào, Cô Lane.

1412
02:34:30,730 --> 02:34:31,690
Xin chào.

1413
02:34:31,780 --> 02:34:33,150
